<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id90357f9f-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6" identifier="/us/usc/t22/s3352"><num value="3352">§ 3352.</num><heading> Establishment</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Subject to <ref href="/us/usc/t22/s2321h">section 2321h of this title</ref>, the President may establish a regional contingency stockpile for Taiwan that consists of munitions and other appropriate defense articles.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id90357fa0-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6">(<ref href="/us/pl/117/263/dE/tLV/s5503/b">Pub. L. 117–263, div. E, title LV, § 5503(b)</ref>, <date date="2022-12-23">Dec. 23, 2022</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/136/3298">136 Stat. 3298</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
